    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2184, the dystopian city of Neo-London is ruled by the iron fist of the One Party. Hope, a young rebel from the prole class, fights to break free from their oppressive control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/31a1e2e46af39681289f1444f1007596.poster.avif?t=1741618341\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/31a1e2e46af39681289f1444f1007596.webm?t=1741618341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/31a1e2e46af39681289f1444f1007596.mp4?t=1741618341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into an intense narrative through parkour, help Hope join the resistance, and dismantle a totalitarian regime. Explore the towering skyscrapers and shadowy alleys of Neo-London, uncovering hidden truths in a city that never sleeps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/b805fd4345a79c4d4409d2fbd0941973.poster.avif?t=1741618341\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/b805fd4345a79c4d4409d2fbd0941973.webm?t=1741618341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179510/extras/b805fd4345a79c4d4409d2fbd0941973.mp4?t=1741618341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a challenge, with secret cassette tapes waiting to be discovered, revealing pieces of Hope's story and the world around her. Can you master every leap and uncover every secret?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acrobatic movements</strong>: Master dynamic parkour skills to turn the city into your playground.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>First-person immersion</strong>: Feel the vertigo of dizzying heights and the fluidity of seamless movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed and agility</strong>: Navigate a futuristic urban world with breathtaking precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A dystopian story</strong>: Uncover the lives of Neo-London's inhabitants and the secrets of its dark history.&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden collectibles</strong>: Find cassette tapes in each level.</p></li></ul>",
